<template>
<User_list msg="Welcome to Your Vue.js App" />
</template>

<script>
import User_list from './components/User_list.vue'
import axios from 'axios'
const baseUrl = 'http://localhost:3000/todos/'

export default {
    name: 'App',
    data() {
        return {
            todos: []
        }
    },
    methods: {
        async axios.get(baseUrl).then(resp => {
            resp.data;
        }).catch(err => {
            console.log(err);
        })
    }
}
</script>
